trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> contains information about the state of a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> contém informações sobre o estado de um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to get a collection of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects that represents the state of the workflow queues associated with a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Você pode chamar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> para obter uma coleção de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objetos que representa o estado das filas de fluxo de trabalho associado a uma instância de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the unconsumed items in the workflow queue.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de itens não consumidos na fila de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> that contains the unconsumed items in the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> que contém os itens não consumidos o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" /> associated with this <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome da <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" /> associada a esta <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection that contains the qualified name each activity subscribed to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção que contém o nome qualificado de cada atividade que assinou a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> that contains the qualified name of the each activity subscribed to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> que contém o nome qualificado de cada atividade assinada o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
